ability.tff.ancient_hammer: Slows enemies on hit. Can also be used as a Diamond pickaxe.
ability.tff.ancient_hatchet: Continuous attacks grant stacking attack speed.
ability.tff.ancient_whistle: Use item to emit a powerful shockwave of sound around you. Any mobs hit will fly away from you. Both yourself and any mobs hit will take armor piercing damage.
ability.tff.angelic_whistle: Use item to create a beautiful harmony of music, launching and lifting all surrounding mobs away from you. Any mobs that hear your music take armor piercing damage.
ability.tff.bone_launcer: Use item to launch a low damage, armor piercing bone projectile.
ability.tff.brittle_branch: Use item to launch multiple poisoned projectiles.
ability.tff.bug_eggs: Use item to summon a collection of friendly Reetles to fight for you.
ability.tff.electric_pickaxe: Breaking an "Underground" block adds a charge, with each charge increasing mining speed. Breaking a non "Underground" block dissipates all charges.
ability.tff.energetic_fungus: Gain Regeneration when you are not moving.
ability.tff.explosive_powder: Use item to violently launch yourself forward.
ability.tff.festering_club: Mobs hit are given Poison and Wither for a short time.
ability.tff.flame_orb: Hold in your Off Hand to apply onhit effects to Fester Forest Magic items.
ability.tff.flesh_ball: Use item to squeeze the ball and give yourself very high regeneration at the expense of your movement speed.
ability.tff.flower_crown: When worn, slain mobs drop more experience.
ability.tff.forgemaster_hammer: The massive weight of the hammer applies large amounts of knockback to any mob hit.
ability.tff.forgemaster_orb: Hold in your Off Hand to apply onhit effects to Fester Forest Magic items.
ability.tff.frost_mallet: Use item to slam the mallet into the ground, dealing 50% of your max health to all nearby mobs.
ability.tff.frostbitten_orb: Hold in your Off Hand to apply onhit effects to Fester Forest Magic items.
ability.tff.frozen_bow: Converts all shot arrows into Icy Arrows. Shoots 3 arrows at a time, for the cost of one. All shot arrows do an additional 20% damage.
ability.tff.frozen_orb: Hold in your Off Hand to apply onhit effects to Fester Forest Magic items.
ability.tff.frozen_pendant: When worn, the charm leeches the movement from nearby mobs, and returns it to the wearer.
ability.tff.glaciated_staff: Use item to launch a massive ice boulder. The boulder explodes on impact, damaging nearby mobs.
ability.tff.glowing_book: Use item to apply Glowing to nearby mobs.
ability.tff.goopy_pickaxe: The goop is able to break any block with diamond efficiency.
ability.tff.ice_book: Use item to launch a projectile at nearby mobs. Crouch while using item to change targeting mode.
ability.tff.icy_bow: Converts all shot arrows into Icy Arrows.
ability.tff.icy_paxel: This tool can break any block with diamond efficiency.
ability.tff.levitate_orb: Hold in your Off Hand to apply onhit effects to Fester Forest Magic items.
ability.tff.life_orb: Hold in your Off Hand to apply onhit effects to Fester Forest Magic items.
ability.tff.life_scythe: Use item to grant yourself absorption and resistance for a short time. This power does, however, make you very hungry...
ability.tff.meteor_wand: Use item on a block or mob to summon a meteor above your head that will land at that location. Does not work well under a roof!
ability.tff.pocket_sand: Use item to throw sand from your pocket, blinding any mobs hit.
ability.tff.poison_orb: Hold in your Off Hand to apply onhit effects to Fester Forest Magic items.
ability.tff.reaver_blade: Hitting a mob afflicts both yourself and the target with the same random effect of a random strength.
ability.tff.reetle_orb: Hold in your Off Hand to apply onhit effects to Fester Forest Magic items.
ability.tff.rotfish_orb: Hold in your Off Hand to apply onhit effects to Fester Forest Magic items.
ability.tff.rotting_catalyst: Used to ignite a portal to the Fester Forest made of Fester Bricks, similar to a Nether portal.
ability.tff.rotting_staff: Use item to launch a rotting bolt.
ability.tff.shadow_bow: Functions as both a bow and a sword, accepting both kinds of enchantments.
ability.tff.shard_of_ice: Use item to launch an icy projectile, dealing the same damage you would with a melee attack.
ability.tff.shield_book: Use item to temporarily grant yourself a large number of Absorption hearts.
ability.tff.shock_sword: Has a chance to paralyze any mob hit.
ability.tff.verdant_branch: Use item on a mob to summon multiple poisoned homing projectiles.
ability.tff.volatile_sword: Use item to emit a burst of flame, damaging and igniting all nearby mobs.
ability.tff.wither_orb: Hold in your Off Hand to apply onhit effects to Fester Forest Magic items.
death.attack.tff_banshee: %1$s blew a whistle a little too hard
death.attack.tff_bone_damage.player: %1$s was knocked out with a bone by %2$s
death.attack.tff_frostbitten_bolt_damage: %1$s was frozen by the Frostbitten King
death.attack.tff_frozen_damage.player: %2$s was pierced by an icicle from %1$s
death.attack.tff_frozen_rock_damage: %1$s was smashed by a large chunk of ice
death.attack.tff_frozen_rock_damage.play: %2$s crushed %1$s with a large chunk of ice
death.attack.tff_goop_acid: %1$s was melted into a slimy puddle
death.attack.tff_goop_acid.player: %2$s turned %1$s into a puddle of slime
death.attack.tff_knockup_damage.player: %1$s was slammed into the ground by %2$s
death.attack.tff_meteor_damage: %1$s was crushed by a flying meteor
death.attack.tff_meteor_damage.player: %1$s was crushed by a flying meteor from %2$s
death.attack.tff_sand_damage: %1$s got too much sand in their eyes
death.attack.tff_volatile_ghost: %1$s played with explosives a little too much
death.attack.tff_volatile_sword: %1$s burned up by a flaming blade
